Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是杀害了休斯准将的子弹
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.60,0:01:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,口径是45mm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只使用了一发
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.78,0:01:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禁不住想夸犯人枪法好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从近距离开的枪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.80,0:01:57.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是女性也可以办到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.19,0:02:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所使用的枪的口径是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.67,0:02:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,45mm口径
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.72,0:02:09.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的子弹补充申请
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:11.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.56,0:02:16.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里写着一发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.88,0:02:18.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用在哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在申请书上也写了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.61,0:02:23.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做爱德华·爱力克护卫的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:24.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五研究所…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.18,0:02:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所已经被封锁了 应该是没人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.17,0:02:33.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那时并非没人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:36.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你的主张
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.82,0:02:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去找使用了的子弹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第五研究所因为迷之爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.45,0:02:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成了瓦砾之山
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:51.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你用枪的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本应是没人的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.00,0:02:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且即使想找子弹 也已经被埋在了瓦砾之下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天 在作案时间前后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.61,0:03:06.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有证人说看到你从现场离开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.91,0:03:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.24,0:03:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.27,0:03:17.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天正在放假 我在父母家里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.11,0:03:20.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请向我的父母确认一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人以及亲密朋友的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:26.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法作为不在场证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:31.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯正在受审
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是长官也无法见面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.69,0:03:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壮少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布鲁斯军曹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.14,0:03:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少佐也来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.79,0:03:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 罗斯少尉的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.55,0:03:50.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 实际上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:56.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上在第五研究所为了爱力克兄弟的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也和少尉一起开了一枪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.52,0:04:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:02.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把这件事情递交了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.48,0:04:03.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没被接受
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准备把少尉弄成犯人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.40,0:04:19.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,950)\fn方正大标宋_GBK\fs135\fsp12\blur6\bord5\1c&H00&\3c&HFFFFFFFF&}冰冷的火焰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看 都是伤痕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常辛苦的旅程呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:37.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后准备怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.77,0:04:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 别哭
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你希望我们怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:09.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这是什么表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:14.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为你们从没找我商量你们自己的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.19,0:05:18.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在休斯先生被杀的危险地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.90,0:05:33.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德和阿尔一直在战斗着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.28,0:05:37.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一想 就觉得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为 说不定会死
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然从我面前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像爸爸和妈妈一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.98,0:05:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一想就觉得非常害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话 想让你们放弃旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.48,0:06:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然想让你们恢复原来的身体
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.27,0:06:11.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也想让你们停止危险的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.54,0:06:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道想怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.13,0:06:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉真温柔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:34.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你在说什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.14,0:06:37.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都很温柔的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 伤痕会变多的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.39,0:06:40.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}（你在说什么呢 真是的）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:47.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚报
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.02,0:06:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.46,0:06:55.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 又是报纸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.65,0:06:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一整天都陪着你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只有这么点乐子了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是法尔蔓准尉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:08.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从外线打的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.80,0:07:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请接通马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.34,0:07:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 代码是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.89,0:07:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么 这么紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.09,0:07:18.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Airam George Oliver 4649
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.68,0:07:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是那时的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贤者之石
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.37,0:07:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有咬尾蛇刺青的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.60,0:07:35.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人造人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.57,0:07:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:41.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.78,0:07:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别吓我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.13,0:07:46.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前台…报纸…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:48.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:53.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.42,0:07:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯少尉被断定为杀害休斯准将的犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.83,0:08:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.20,0:08:06.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐或少佐也许知道点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温莉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.53,0:08:16.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.79,0:08:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是小狗的项圈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.13,0:08:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 再问你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真的是15岁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.50,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别骗人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.42,0:08:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.37,0:08:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是入侵者 快来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.21,0:08:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乖乖待着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.90,0:08:44.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没劲 没劲 没劲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.07,0:08:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有没有干劲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:50.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枪不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.65,0:08:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让开 你这…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 不能砍就是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.42,0:09:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 枪不起作用的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我从这里放出去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:16.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从清国来的非法入境者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.39,0:09:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这么大老远跑来真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.76,0:09:24.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把我放出去我就帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.90,0:09:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没时间和你玩…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.38,0:09:30.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说哪个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.07,0:09:32.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东边的清国
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.52,0:09:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.52,0:09:46.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.78,0:09:55.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈罗 甜心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.73,0:09:57.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在第五研究所的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.28,0:10:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能记得真让我高兴呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:10.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是每次看到右手被枪打的洞就会想起那时候的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀害休斯的大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.66,0:10:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是误会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.15,0:10:16.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报纸可是写着确定是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.08,0:10:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.59,0:10:26.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样下去肯定是被套上罪名接受枪决
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.80,0:10:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要仔细调查的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.59,0:10:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你选择吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.78,0:10:34.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是等着被乱枪射死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:36.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是和我一起逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.47,0:10:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二选一
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.15,0:10:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.24,0:10:45.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此以外没有选择了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:47.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来是没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 爸爸 妈妈 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:10:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.69,0:11:00.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.33,0:11:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好做好护卫 你这个笨蛋骨头铠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 气势不错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是要胆子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通知市内全区
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.69,0:11:20.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽亚·罗斯越狱了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.65,0:11:23.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎有凶恶的共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立即抓捕归案
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.73,0:11:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果抵抗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.29,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允许射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要逃到哪里去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要多问 跑就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.40,0:11:43.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.17,0:11:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.39,0:11:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.45,0:11:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连麟也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.13,0:11:53.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.20,0:11:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.30,0:11:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我要问的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:58.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 没时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.19,0:12:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从那边的胡同里一直走就能逃到仓库街
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:06.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉着那里的黑暗应该能逃脱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.62,0:12:09.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉 休斯中佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.08,0:12:13.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 宪兵来了的话 会被射杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.05,0:12:14.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.93,0:12:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉 罗斯少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玛丽亚·罗斯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:44.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.33,0:12:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得手了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.85,0:12:48.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.01,0:12:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真危险
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.94,0:12:53.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走了 一线眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…麟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.85,0:12:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么和那种家伙在一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.74,0:12:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后再告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.07,0:13:02.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.75,0:13:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 钢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.88,0:13:22.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.17,0:13:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休斯中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.06,0:13:47.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会被罗斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:49.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不告诉我？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:13:57.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然对长官出手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.45,0:13:59.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掂量一下自己有几斤重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.78,0:14:10.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.86,0:14:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:12.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个家伙把罗斯少尉…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.68,0:14:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,罗斯少尉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.99,0:14:23.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.75,0:14:28.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面有令 射杀越狱的玛丽亚·罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.69,0:14:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.86,0:14:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么叫仅此而已？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.16,0:14:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于隐瞒休斯之死的事情 我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.12,0:14:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是别对命令提出异议
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.62,0:14:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得要求解释
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实地遵从
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是军队
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:57.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.77,0:15:00.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说明一下这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:06.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面应该有令 如果抵抗就可以射杀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:09.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为抵抗了 所以杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:14.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说准将是你的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:15.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:23.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让罗斯少尉越狱的不会是你的手下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.53,0:15:27.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了亲手烧死她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要主观地判断事物
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:52.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没把休斯准将的死讯告诉你们 真是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:56.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.97,0:16:01.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别想太多
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.53,0:16:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全到齐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.88,0:16:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诺克斯医生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,损伤实在太严重了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.42,0:16:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是从勉强留下的牙齿治疗痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以断定这个人是玛丽亚·罗斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.56,0:16:22.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.80,0:16:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把这个美人弄成了炭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.72,0:16:31.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你对她有很深的仇恨呢 马斯坦古
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.33,0:16:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报了仇 满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到伊修瓦尔战的英雄会对一个小姑娘下这样的毒手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.63,0:16:47.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想吐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.13,0:16:58.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大佐 这次我的部下做了非常不该的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.66,0:17:03.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到罗斯少尉会杀人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.25,0:17:07.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是个很诚实 很认真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有同情心的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.19,0:17:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你是疲劳积累得太多了 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.25,0:17:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去休假吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.20,0:17:33.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我曾经住过东部 那里不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有都会的喧嚣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.90,0:17:38.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且美人很多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.04,0:17:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.62,0:17:52.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马斯坦古漂亮地替挚友报了仇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.85,0:17:54.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可喜可贺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.99,0:17:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.28,0:18:00.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是为了让大佐安分的作战吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.92,0:18:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么不好？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.16,0:18:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗把饵吃了也是不错的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 他似乎引起了其他人的不满
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.63,0:18:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也会被部下抛弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.09,0:18:16.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.89,0:18:17.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休假申请
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这个时期吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.22,0:18:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 可以
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.82,0:18:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.50,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然擅自出门
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.34,0:18:46.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被发现了的话 不知道大佐会怎么教训我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.17,0:18:50.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来的时候没有被人看到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.36,0:18:52.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.23,0:18:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被凶恶的犯人抓住的可怜军人 这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.53,0:19:00.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 从刚才开始你在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.25,0:19:06.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼烟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狼烟？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 把不认识的人带来 你到底在想些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少主 真让我们好找
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.57,0:19:16.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真快呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人变多了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.83,0:19:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊莉莎白 还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.89,0:19:27.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你经常给我打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.20,0:19:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常偷懒的话会惹你那可怕的副官生气的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.39,0:19:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧 她休假了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.97,0:19:39.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托这个福 我能往你那里打电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:42.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么看那个？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.49,0:19:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中尉休假后马上就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.38,0:19:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人真的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.58,0:19:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,监护人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.62,0:19:51.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:55.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到了这里以后一直没有休假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.37,0:19:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差不多想拿个假期
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.42,0:19:59.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出门吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.61,0:20:02.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近迷上了钓鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.17,0:20:05.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.85,0:20:18.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了 是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你突然干什么 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.13,0:20:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好 你的机械铠坏掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.20,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是重大事态
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须马上修理
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我负责把你送到利塞布尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.52,0:20:48.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回利塞布尔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 阿尔 听我说啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿尔冯斯·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.71,0:20:58.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太显眼了 请留在中央都市
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.98,0:21:01.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 马上就准备火车
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:04.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们走 爱德华·爱力克
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,适可而止吧 少佐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.08,0:21:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这也是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.78,0:21:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个男人的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.18,0:21:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 了解了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.27,0:21:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姆斯壮少佐和爱德华·爱力克坐上火车了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.48,0:21:29.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.40,0:21:34.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来碍事的人就没了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.79,0:21:45.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我见了拘留所袭击犯的目击者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是犯人的画像
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.01,0:21:51.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还活着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和火焰之大佐有联系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.55,0:21:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 可能性很大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.02,0:21:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:04.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 他不仅逃得很快而且藏得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.40,0:22:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.64,0:22:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真无能
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.67,0:22:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人 大妈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:11.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手不够
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.41,0:22:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.52,0:22:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人手的话 有这个就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.13,0:22:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 该你出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刽子手巴利
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.05,0:24:03.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切的真实都在克塞鲁克塞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.56,0:24:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在渐渐腐朽消亡之城市的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.76,0:24:10.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拂拭了少年的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.63,0:24:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 钢之链金术师
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.26,0:24:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.93,0:24:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第十八话 渺小人类的傲慢手掌
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.34,0:24:25.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类哟 升起反击的狼烟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【OP】
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.82,0:00:06.16,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\blur4}纯白的景色在向我招手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:12.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,1000)\blur4}我即将起程   前往那未知的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.43,0:00:21.62,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}迷茫的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.65,0:00:24.43,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在灰色的天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:30.51,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}在不断变化的地图里 搀杂着各种梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:32.90,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}总有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:36.93,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}即使以我这微小的步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:43.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}也能走到那云的彼端吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.02,0:00:44.65,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.65,0:00:46.19,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}却受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.25,0:00:49.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}仿佛看透了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}从天上落下的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.83,0:00:53.01,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}点点雨水
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.01,0:00:56.22,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}反复的漫反射
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.26,0:00:59.08,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}笔直的光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.08,0:01:01.80,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}相互交叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.86,0:01:05.39,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}并不知道去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.39,0:01:06.68,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}只管
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.68,0:01:08.25,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}不停地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:14.09,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}淡淡的残影烙印在两眼中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.09,0:01:16.02,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur4}在这片天空下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.02,0:01:19.83,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)\blur4}无论身在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.28,0:01:22.14,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\blur4}一定可以到达
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.14,0:01:26.95,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)\blur4}那未曾见过的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,【ED】
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.64,0:22:33.32,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\fsp-1.5\fnRoman\fs35\b1}Let it all out, Let it all out
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.32,0:22:37.42,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}不必故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:44.20,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人这样描绘
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.20,0:22:50.00,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在墙上涂鸦的花也会摇动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.00,0:22:55.60,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人知道真正的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.60,0:22:57.88,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在漫长的路途中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.88,0:23:01.30,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去与获取
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.30,0:23:08.99,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}突然寂寞  也有哭泣的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.07,0:23:16.50,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼泪也好  痛苦也好  都将化为恒星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.50,0:23:22.48,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,点燃照亮明天的灯火
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:27.64,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,举起小手  两个人一起创造
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:32.85,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去搜寻星尘与光芒四射的永远…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.85,0:23:38.22,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见 那天也许还会降临
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:44.16,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}即使季节依然在不断地交替
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算有点迷茫  也要向前
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.24,0:23:52.28,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与你一起前行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:56.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,1000)}请让我维持到永远

